{"tid":2316903,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始，即使已與疫情搏鬥近一整年，仍然戴反口罩","createTime":"2020-12-08T07:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T09:22:29.000Z","uid":241764,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"caea5c9d4c4e12b861efe0c766666d1022748005","tid":2316903,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"政府今日（8 日）公布一系列防疫措施，包括「禁足令」法律框架、食肆禁晚市堂食、關閉表列處所如健身中心等。<br />\n但記者在記者會上發現，作為政府「防疫之首」的食物及衞生局局長陳肇始，即使已與疫情搏鬥近一整年，仍然戴反口罩。現場可見，其口罩的「風琴位」向上，或令更多飛沫或病毒殘留在其上。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">陳肇始是註冊護士，亦是護理學教授。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/130082820_3711532658932327_6267145280076703324_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=t-oPZrh7jswAX8JQSjz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=2a57bc922811aa04dd8c5724eaac7ced&amp;oe=5FF302FD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F130082820_3711532658932327_6267145280076703324_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dt-oPZrh7jswAX8JQSjz%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D2a57bc922811aa04dd8c5724eaac7ced%26oe%3D5FF302FD&h=d788d536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cd6b62ec30fc1c628244630a2db1c2d32fed2ea","tid":2316903,"uid":64345,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgHkYFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgHkYFH.png&h=07c9c90d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5203ced793e4bffcf97e3646dc1cf3e7298397f","tid":2316903,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"佢喺前線做護士都唔知有冇10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁上下<p class=\"center\"></p>"},{"pid":"c385d068be5bb0546357b31cb9317c21bd40ba95","tid":2316903,"uid":132302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT